{"id":933,"parent_id":926,"book_id":1,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":933,"title":"Micah 7","subtitle":"","short_title":"Micah","uri":"/scriptures/ot/micah/7","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 7"],[".studySummary",["i","Though the people of Israel have rebelled, yet in the last days the Lord will have mercy on them—He will have compassion and pardon their iniquities."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/ot/micah/7.1","order":"02.34.007.62120"},["b","1"],"Woe is me! for I am as when they have gathered the summer fruits, as the grapegleanings of the vintage:",["i","there is"],"no cluster to eat: my soul desired the firstripe fruit."],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/ot/micah/7.2","order":"02.34.007.62121"},["b","2"],"The good",["i","man"],"is perished out of the earth: and",["i","there is"],"none upright among men: they all lie in wait for blood; they hunt every man his",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_2a"},"brother"],"with a net."],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/ot/micah/7.3","order":"02.34.007.62122"},["b","3"],"¶That they may do evil with both hands earnestly, the prince asketh, and the judge",["i","asketh"],"for a reward; and the great",["i","man,"],"he uttereth his mischievous desire: so they wrap it up."],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/ot/micah/7.4","order":"02.34.007.62123"},["b","4"],"The best of them",["i","is"],"as a brier: the most upright",["i","is sharper"],"than a thorn hedge: the day of thy watchmen",["i","and"],"thy",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_4a"},"visitation"],"cometh; now shall be their perplexity."],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/ot/micah/7.5","order":"02.34.007.62124"},["b","5"],"¶",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_5a"},"Trust"],"ye not in a friend, put ye not confidence in a guide: keep the doors of thy mouth from her that lieth in thy bosom."],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/ot/micah/7.6","order":"02.34.007.62125"},["b","6"],"For the son dishonoureth the father, the daughter riseth up against her mother, the daughter in law against her mother in law; a man’s",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_6a"},"enemies"],["i","are"],"the men of his own",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_6b"},"house"],"."],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/ot/micah/7.7","order":"02.34.007.62126"},["b","7"],"Therefore I will look unto the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"; I will wait for the God of my salvation: my God will",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_7a"},"hear"],"me."],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/ot/micah/7.8","order":"02.34.007.62127"},["b","8"],"¶Rejoice not against me, O mine enemy: when I fall, I shall arise; when I sit in",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_8a"},"darkness"],", the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],["i","shall be"],"a",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_8b"},"light"],"unto me."],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/ot/micah/7.9","order":"02.34.007.62128"},["b","9"],"I will",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_9a"},"bear"],"the indignation of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],", because I have sinned against him, until he plead my cause, and execute judgment for me: he will bring me forth to the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_9b"},"light"],",",["i","and"],"I shall behold his righteousness."],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/ot/micah/7.10","order":"02.34.007.62129"},["b","10"],"Then",["i","she that is"],"mine enemy shall see",["i","it,"],"and shame shall cover her which said unto me, Where is the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"thy God? mine eyes shall behold her: now shall she be",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_10a"},"trodden"],"down as the mire of the streets."],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/ot/micah/7.11","order":"02.34.007.62130"},["b","11"],["i","In"],"the day that thy walls are to be built,",["i","in"],"that day shall the decree be far removed."],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/ot/micah/7.12","order":"02.34.007.62131"},["b","12"],["i","In"],"that day",["i","also"],"he shall",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_12a"},"come"],"even to thee from Assyria, and",["i","from"],"the fortified cities, and from the fortress even to the river, and from sea to sea, and",["i","from"],"mountain to mountain."],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/ot/micah/7.13","order":"02.34.007.62132"},["b","13"],"Notwithstanding the land shall be desolate because of them that dwell therein, for the fruit of their doings."],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/ot/micah/7.14","order":"02.34.007.62133"},["b","14"],"¶Feed thy people with thy rod, the flock of thine heritage, which dwell solitarily",["i","in"],"the wood, in the midst of Carmel: let them feed",["i","in"],"Bashan and Gilead, as in the days of old."],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/ot/micah/7.15","order":"02.34.007.62134"},["b","15"],"According to the days of thy coming out of the land of Egypt will I shew unto him marvellous",["i","things."]],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/ot/micah/7.16","order":"02.34.007.62135"},["b","16"],"¶The nations shall see and be confounded at all their might: they shall lay",["i","their"],"hand upon",["i","their"],"mouth, their ears shall be deaf."],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/ot/micah/7.17","order":"02.34.007.62136"},["b","17"],"They shall lick the dust like a serpent, they shall move out of their holes like worms of the earth: they shall be afraid of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"our God, and shall fear because of thee."],["div",{"id":"18","uri":"/scriptures/ot/micah/7.18","order":"02.34.007.62137"},["b","18"],"Who",["i","is"],"a God like unto thee, that",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_18a"},"pardoneth"],"iniquity, and passeth by the transgression of the remnant of his heritage? he retaineth not his",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_18b"},"anger"],"for ever, because he",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_18c"},"delighteth"],["i","in"],["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_18d"},"mercy"],"."],["div",{"id":"19","uri":"/scriptures/ot/micah/7.19","order":"02.34.007.62138"},["b","19"],"He will turn again, he will have",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_19a"},"compassion"],"upon us; he will subdue our iniquities; and thou wilt cast all their sins into the depths of the sea."],["div",{"id":"20","uri":"/scriptures/ot/micah/7.20","order":"02.34.007.62139"},["b","20"],"Thou wilt perform the truth to Jacob,",["i","and"],"the mercy to",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_20a"},"Abraham"],", which thou hast",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_20b"},"sworn"],"unto our fathers from the days of old."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"2a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/micah/7.2a","order":"02.34.007.62140"},["b","2a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/9.19"},"Isa. 9:19"],"."],["div",{"id":"4a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/micah/7.4a","order":"02.34.007.62142"},["b","4a"],["span.small","IE"],"punishment."],["div",{"id":"5a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/micah/7.5a","order":"02.34.007.62144"},["b","5a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/9.4"},"Jer. 9:4"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/trust-not-in-the-arm-of-flesh"},"TG Trust Not in the Arm of Flesh"],"."],["div",{"id":"6a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/micah/7.6a","order":"02.34.007.62146"},["b","6a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/luke/12.53"},"Luke 12:53"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/enemies"},"TG Enemies"],"."],["div",{"id":"6b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/micah/7.6b","order":"02.34.007.62148"},["b","6b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/matt/10.36.35-36"},"Matt. 10:36 (35–36)"],"."],["div",{"id":"7a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/micah/7.7a","order":"02.34.007.62150"},["b","7a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ps/4.1.1,3"},"Ps. 4:1 (1, 3)"],"."],["div",{"id":"8a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/micah/7.8a","order":"02.34.007.62152"},["b","8a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/darkness-spiritual"},"TG Darkness, Spiritual"],"."],["div",{"id":"8b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/micah/7.8b","order":"02.34.007.62154"},["b","8b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/jesus-christ-light-of-the-world"},"TG Jesus Christ, Light of the World"],"."],["div",{"id":"9a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/micah/7.9a","order":"02.34.007.62156"},["b","9a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/lam/3.27.24-27"},"Lam. 3:27 (24–27)"],"."],["div",{"id":"9b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/micah/7.9b","order":"02.34.007.62158"},["b","9b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/16.4.4-5"},"3 Ne. 16:4 (4–5)"],"."],["div",{"id":"10a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/micah/7.10a","order":"02.34.007.62160"},["b","10a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/mal/4.3"},"Mal. 4:3"],"."],["div",{"id":"12a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/micah/7.12a","order":"02.34.007.62162"},["b","12a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/neh/1.9"},"Neh. 1:9"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/101.13"},"D&C 101:13"],"."],["div",{"id":"18a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/micah/7.18a","order":"02.34.007.62164"},["b","18a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/forgive"},"TG Forgive"],"."],["div",{"id":"18b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/micah/7.18b","order":"02.34.007.62166"},["b","18b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/57.16"},"Isa. 57:16"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/3.5.1-5"},"Jer. 3:5 (1–5)"],"."],["div",{"id":"18c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/micah/7.18c","order":"02.34.007.62168"},["b","18c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/9.24"},"Jer. 9:24"],"."],["div",{"id":"18d","uri":"/scriptures/ot/micah/7.18d","order":"02.34.007.62170"},["b","18d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/god-mercy-of"},"TG God, Mercy of"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/mercy"},"Mercy"],"."],["div",{"id":"19a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/micah/7.19a","order":"02.34.007.62172"},["b","19a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/64.2"},"D&C 64:2"],"."],["div",{"id":"20a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/micah/7.20a","order":"02.34.007.62174"},["b","20a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/29.14"},"2 Ne. 29:14"],"."],["div",{"id":"20b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/micah/7.20b","order":"02.34.007.62176"},["b","20b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/luke/1.55.54-55"},"Luke 1:55 (54–55)"],",",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/luke/1.72"},"72"],"."]]}
